Package: ramgcl
Type: Package
Title: Iteratively solve large linear systems using the amgcl library. 
Version: 0.1
Date: 2017-06-26
Author: Simon Barthelme
Maintainer: Simon Barthelme <simon.barthelme@gipsa-lab.fr>
Description: amgcl by D. Demidov is a library for solving large, sparse linear systems using iterative methods. This package allows you to call amgcl from R. 
License: MIT 
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.11),
    RcppEigen (>= 0.3.2.9.0),
    purrr
Depends:
    Matrix,
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
